text.tspan: Detail Reports feature is a management-level tool accessed via the
Web Browser, designed to provide deep analytical insight into fleet
expenditures. It enables Management to generate detailed,
filterable reports by criteria such as date range, Driver Name, and
Car Number. The reports present specific cost breakdowns (e.g.,
Toll fees and Fuel volume/price) and are exportable to Excel or PDF,
critically supporting operational cost analysis and strategic
The Driver & Car Data feature is the centralized data management
function, executed by Dispatchers and Management via the Web
Browser. It encompasses Driver Registration, Car Registration, and
related CA Registration, serving as the essential and accurate database
foundation required for all fleet transactions, system security, and
detailed reporting per driver or vehicle.
